Algorithm	Current Status	Main Use
SHA-256	✅ Most Used	Malware analysis, EDR, VirusTotal, file integrity, digital signatures
MD5	⚠️ Legacy but still everywhere	Legacy malware databases, IOC feeds, quick file identification
SHA-1	⚠️ Legacy	Older malware reports, Git history, compatibility
SHA-512	✅ Common	High-security environments, certificates, file verification
SHA-3	✅ Modern but less common	Specialized cryptographic applications
BLAKE2 / BLAKE3	✅ Growing	Fast integrity checks, storage, backups
Argon2	✅ Standard	Password hashing
bcrypt	✅ Very Common	Password hashing in web applications
PBKDF2	✅ Very Common	Password hashing, encryption key derivation
